-- 蕭何 Act 1 stub: 沛の主吏として劉邦を見る
def colorMiao := "#7a5a8a"

def xiaoheAct1 := [
  narr("bg-pei", "紀元前 209 年、沛。主吏・蕭何の朝は、劉邦の尻拭いから始まる。", "BCE 209, Pei. Chief clerk Xiao He's morning begins, as always, with cleaning up after Liu Bang."),
  think("bg-pei", "蕭何", colorXiao,
    "「また劉殿の帳簿が合わぬ。十文ほどの誤差。叱ろうか――いや、放っておこう」",
    "“Master Liu's ledger doesn't reconcile. About ten coins off. Should I scold him — no, let it pass.“",
    "なぜか、あの男の前では『正しさ』が貧相に見える。何だろう、この感覚は。", "For some reason, in front of that man, 'rightness' looks shabby. What is this feeling?"),
